WEBVTT

00:13:58.017 --> 00:14:01.096
Where you have a very large
part of your economy

00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:02.277
being informal,

00:14:02.301 --> 00:14:06.041
where people live hand-to-mouth every day,

00:14:06.493 --> 00:14:11.014
the lockdowns we have
in advanced economies

00:14:11.038 --> 00:14:12.847
are not quite applicable,

00:14:12.871 --> 00:14:14.442
but even there,

00:14:14.466 --> 00:14:18.778
countries are doing really well
in social distancing

00:14:18.802 --> 00:14:20.902
to the extent it is possible.

00:14:21.466 --> 00:14:23.807
Many of the countries in Africa

00:14:23.831 --> 00:14:27.537
were very early to step up
preventive measures.

00:14:27.561 --> 00:14:28.720
Why?

00:14:28.744 --> 00:14:31.528
They learned from the Ebola,
they learned from prior crises